JO  - Temporal Representation and Reasoning (TIME), 2012 19th International Symposium on
TI  - Temporal Implications of Database Information Accountability
T2  - Temporal Representation and Reasoning (TIME), 2012 19th International Symposium on
IS  - 
SN  - 1530-1311
