TI  - Provenance-Aware Tracing ofWorm Break-in and Contaminations: A Process Coloring Approach
T2  - Distributed Computing Systems, 2006. ICDCS 2006. 26th IEEE International Conference on
IS  - 
SN  - 1063-6927
VO  - 
SP  - 38
EP  - 38
AU  - Xuxian Jiang
