JO  - Computer Security Applications Conference, 2001. ACSAC 2001. Proceedings 17th Annual
TI  - eXpert-BSM: a host-based intrusion detection solution for Sun Solaris
T2  - Computer Security Applications Conference, 2001. ACSAC 2001. Proceedings 17th Annual
IS  - 
