JO  - Computer Security Foundations Workshop VII, 1994. CSFW 7. Proceedings
TI  - Redrawing the security perimeter of a trusted system
T2  - Computer Security Foundations Workshop VII, 1994. CSFW 7. Proceedings
IS  - 
SN  - 1063-6900
VO  - 
SP  - 162
EP  - 174
AU  - Sterne, D.F.
AU  - Benson, G.S.
