TI  - An effective auditing scheme for cloud computing
T2  - Global Communications Conference (GLOBECOM), 2012 IEEE
IS  - 
SN  - 1930-529X
VO  - 
SP  - 1599
EP  - 1604
AU  - Houlihan, R.
AU  - Xiaojiang Du
