TI  - Identifying Compromised Users in Shared Computing Infrastructures: A Data-Driven Bayesian Network Approach
T2  - Reliable Distributed Systems (SRDS), 2011 30th IEEE Symposium on
IS  - 
SN  - 1060-9857
