JO  - Computer Security Foundations Symposium, 2008. CSF '08. IEEE 21st
TI  - Evidence-Based Audit
T2  - Computer Security Foundations Symposium, 2008. CSF '08. IEEE 21st
IS  - 
SN  - 1940-1434
