TI  - Trusted Anonymous Execution: A Model to Raise Trust in Cloud
T2  - Grid and Cooperative Computing (GCC), 2010 9th International Conference on
IS  - 
SN  - 
VO  - 
SP  - 133
EP  - 138
AU  - Zhexuan Song
AU  - Molina, J.
