JO  - Intelligent Networking and Collaborative Systems (INCoS), 2013 5th International Conference on
TI  - Security Analysis of Gagne et al.'s Threshold Attribute-Based Signcryption Scheme
T2  - Intelligent Networking and Collaborative Systems (INCoS), 2013 5th International Conference on
IS  - 
SN  - 
VO  - 
SP  - 103
EP  - 108
AU  - Chang-Ji Wang
