JO  - Software Engineering, IEEE Transactions on
TI  - State transition analysis: a rule-based intrusion detection approach
T2  - Software Engineering, IEEE Transactions on
IS  - 3
SN  - 0098-5589
VO  - 21
SP  - 181
EP  - 199
AU  - Ilgun, K.
AU  - Kemmerer, R.A.
