JO  - Communications, Circuits and Systems, 2007. ICCCAS 2007. International Conference on
TI  - Minining Intrusion Detection Alarms with an SA-based Clustering Approach
T2  - Communications, Circuits and Systems, 2007. ICCCAS 2007. International Conference on
IS  - 
SN  - 
VO  - 
SP  - 905
EP  - 909
AU  - Jianxin Wang
AU  - Yunqing Xia
AU  - Hongzhou Wang
Y1  - 11-13 July 2007
