JO  - Communications and Networks, Journal of
TI  - A secure web-based global management system for firewall/VPN devices
T2  - Communications and Networks, Journal of
IS  - 1
SN  - 1229-2370
VO  - 4
SP  - 71
EP  - 78
AU  - Choi, Mi-Jung
AU  - Hong, James Won-Ki
