JO  - Tsinghua Science and Technology
TI  - Collaborative network security in multi-tenant data center for cloud computing
T2  - Tsinghua Science and Technology
IS  - 1
SN  - 
VO  - 19
SP  - 82
EP  - 94
AU  - Chen, Zhen
AU  - Dong, Wenyu
